### ===========================================
### Health Check (public endpoint)
### ===========================================

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### ===========================================
### Game Server API (requires ADMIN role)
### ===========================================

### Get all game servers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Get game server by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Create a new game server
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

{
  "name": "My Game Server",
  "nitradoId": 12345678
}

### Start a game server
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}/start
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Stop a game server (without message)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}/stop
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Stop a game server (with message)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}/stop
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

{
  "message": "Server maintenance - back in 30 minutes"
}

### Restart a game server (without message)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}/restart
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Restart a game server (with message)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/game-servers/{{serverId}}/restart
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

{
  "message": "Server restart for updates"
}

### ===========================================
### Cron Job Endpoints (requires ADMIN or CRON_JOB role)
### ===========================================

### Trigger game server sync (as cron-job user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/sync-servers
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{cronJobUsername}} {{cronJobPassword}}

### Trigger game server sync (as admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/sync-servers
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminUsername}} {{adminPassword}}

### Update Discord presence (as cron-job user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/update-discord-presence
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{cronJobUsername}} {{cronJobPassword}}
